{"tid":1692350,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"又有「真」黃金店等大家懲罰","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T04:58:26.000Z","uid":337314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12cf7addecc981c477616f493b76ceca4129bd61","tid":1692350,"uid":337314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"話說，太子東喜茶因為擔心大家唔知佢黃，畢竟從未表態同罷工，在心中既野好難估架麻，於是決定係連登表明心跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由9月中起佢地開始用3個account<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>「飄忽極度撚」「太子爺」「廟街大波驊（前身大BB)」</strong></span>，扮手足/街坊係連登曲線話間舖黃，可能睇到既人唔夠多幫唔到手，於10月23日終於要係IG表白自己支持香港既真心真意，然後開始係舖頭貼pepe，早幾日重係蘋果訪問度鬧爆黑警同港鐵搞到生意大跌9成，為公義發聲，重強調自己唔係消費個運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁幫手既黃金店大家快D去懲罰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯貓尾post 1:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【南華早報】太子街坊世界第一！</strong></span><br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581165</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯貓尾post 2:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同我一齊食爆啲良心黃店佢 唔好再比冷血藍店生存到</strong></span><br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593902</a></ins><br />\nPosts #655 #752 #765 #767 #768<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯貓尾post 3:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(借朋友ac) 好嬲 今日無啦啦有個鬼佬入左我地舖 之後撕爛晒d文宣</strong></span><br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1684758</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯貓尾post 4:</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街！太子老虎堂竟然咁刻薄</span></strong><br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank